#. <section class="sutta" id="an4.11"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.11:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.11:0.2"
msgid "2. Caravagga"
msgstr "2. Walking"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: carantasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an4.11:0.3"
msgid "11. Carasutta"
msgstr "11. Walking"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an4.11:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Carato cepi, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno uppajjati kāmavitakko vā byāpādavitakko "
"vā vihiṃsāvitakko vā."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, suppose a mendicant has a sensual, malicious, or cruel thought "
"while walking."

#. VAR: byantīkaroti → vyantikaroti (pts1) | byantiṃ karoti (mr)
msgctxt "an4.11:1.2"
msgid ""
"Tañce bhikkhu adhivāseti, nappajahati na vinodeti na byantīkaroti na "
"anabhāvaṃ gameti, carampi, bhikkhave, bhikkhu evaṃbhūto ‘anātāpī anottāpī "
"satataṃ samitaṃ kusīto hīnavīriyo’ti vuccati."
msgstr ""
"They tolerate it and don’t give it up, get rid of it, eliminate it, and "
"obliterate it. Such a mendicant is said to be ‘not keen or prudent, always "
"lazy, and lacking energy’ when walking."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an4.11:2.1"
msgid ""
"Ṭhitassa cepi, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno uppajjati kāmavitakko vā byāpādavitakko "
"vā vihiṃsāvitakko vā."
msgstr ""
"Suppose a mendicant has a sensual, malicious, or cruel thought while "
"standing …"

msgctxt "an4.11:2.2"
msgid ""
"Tañce bhikkhu adhivāseti, nappajahati na vinodeti na byantīkaroti na "
"anabhāvaṃ gameti, ṭhitopi, bhikkhave, bhikkhu evaṃbhūto ‘anātāpī anottāpī "
"satataṃ samitaṃ kusīto hīnavīriyo’ti vuccati."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an4.11:3.1"
msgid ""
"Nisinnassa cepi, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno uppajjati kāmavitakko vā "
"byāpādavitakko vā vihiṃsāvitakko vā."
msgstr "sitting …"

msgctxt "an4.11:3.2"
msgid ""
"Tañce bhikkhu adhivāseti, nappajahati na vinodeti na byantīkaroti na "
"anabhāvaṃ gameti, nisinnopi, bhikkhave, bhikkhu evaṃbhūto ‘anātāpī anottāpī "
"satataṃ samitaṃ kusīto hīnavīriyo’ti vuccati."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an4.11:4.1"
msgid ""
"Sayānassa cepi, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno jāgarassa uppajjati kāmavitakko vā "
"byāpādavitakko vā vihiṃsāvitakko vā."
msgstr "or lying down while awake."

msgctxt "an4.11:4.2"
msgid ""
"Tañce bhikkhu adhivāseti, nappajahati na vinodeti na byantīkaroti na "
"anabhāvaṃ gameti, sayānopi, bhikkhave, bhikkhu jāgaro evaṃbhūto ‘anātāpī "
"anottāpī satataṃ samitaṃ kusīto hīnavīriyo’ti vuccati."
msgstr ""
"They tolerate it and don’t give it up, get rid of it, eliminate it, and "
"obliterate it. Such a mendicant is said to be ‘not keen or prudent, always "
"lazy, and lacking energy’ when lying down while awake."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an4.11:5.1"
msgid ""
"Carato cepi, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno uppajjati kāmavitakko vā byāpādavitakko vā "
"vihiṃsāvitakko vā."
msgstr ""
"Suppose a mendicant has a sensual, malicious, or cruel thought while walking."

msgctxt "an4.11:5.2"
msgid ""
"Tañce bhikkhu nādhivāseti, pajahati vinodeti byantīkaroti anabhāvaṃ gameti;"
msgstr ""
"They don’t tolerate it, but give it up, get rid of it, eliminate it, and "
"obliterate it."

msgctxt "an4.11:5.3"
msgid ""
"carampi, bhikkhave, bhikkhu evaṃbhūto ‘ātāpī ottāpī satataṃ samitaṃ "
"āraddhavīriyo pahitatto’ti vuccati."
msgstr ""
"Such a mendicant is said to be ‘keen and prudent, always energetic and "
"determined’ when walking."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an4.11:6.1"
msgid ""
"Ṭhitassa cepi, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno uppajjati kāmavitakko vā byāpādavitakko "
"vā vihiṃsāvitakko vā."
msgstr ""
"Suppose a mendicant has a sensual, malicious, or cruel thought while "
"standing …"

msgctxt "an4.11:6.2"
msgid ""
"Tañce bhikkhu nādhivāseti, pajahati vinodeti byantīkaroti anabhāvaṃ gameti;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.11:6.3"
msgid ""
"ṭhitopi, bhikkhave, bhikkhu evaṃbhūto ‘ātāpī ottāpī satataṃ samitaṃ "
"āraddhavīriyo pahitatto’ti vuccati."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "an4.11:7.1"
msgid ""
"Nisinnassa cepi, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno uppajjati kāmavitakko vā "
"byāpādavitakko vā vihiṃsāvitakko vā."
msgstr "sitting …"

msgctxt "an4.11:7.2"
msgid ""
"Tañce bhikkhu nādhivāseti, pajahati vinodeti byantīkaroti anabhāvaṃ gameti;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.11:7.3"
msgid ""
"nisinnopi, bhikkhave, bhikkhu evaṃbhūto ‘ātāpī ottāpī satataṃ samitaṃ "
"āraddhavīriyo pahitatto’ti vuccati."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.14"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "an4.11:8.1"
msgid ""
"Sayānassa cepi, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno jāgarassa uppajjati kāmavitakko vā "
"byāpādavitakko vā vihiṃsāvitakko vā."
msgstr "or lying down while awake."

msgctxt "an4.11:8.2"
msgid ""
"Tañce bhikkhu nādhivāseti, pajahati vinodeti byantīkaroti anabhāvaṃ gameti;"
msgstr ""
"They don’t tolerate it, but give it up, get rid of it, eliminate it, and "
"obliterate it."

msgctxt "an4.11:8.3"
msgid ""
"sayānopi, bhikkhave, bhikkhu jāgaro evaṃbhūto ‘ātāpī ottāpī satataṃ samitaṃ "
"āraddhavīriyo pahitatto’ti vuccatīti."
msgstr ""
"Such a mendicant is said to be ‘keen and prudent, always energetic and "
"determined’ when lying down while awake.”"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "an4.11:9.1"
msgid "Caraṃ vā yadi vā tiṭṭhaṃ,"
msgstr "Whether walking or standing,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.11:9.2"
msgid "nisinno uda vā sayaṃ;"
msgstr "sitting or lying down,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.11:9.3"
msgid "Yo vitakkaṃ vitakketi,"
msgstr "if you think a bad thought"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.11:9.4"
msgid "pāpakaṃ gehanissitaṃ."
msgstr "to do with the lay life,"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "an4.11:10.1"
msgid "Kummaggappaṭipanno so,"
msgstr "you’re on the wrong path,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.11:10.2"
msgid "Mohaneyyesu mucchito;"
msgstr "lost among things that delude."

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.11:10.3"
msgid "Abhabbo tādiso bhikkhu,"
msgstr "Such a mendicant is incapable"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.11:10.4"
msgid "Phuṭṭhuṃ sambodhimuttamaṃ."
msgstr "of touching the highest awakening."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "an4.11:11.1"
msgid "Yo ca caraṃ vā tiṭṭhaṃ vā,"
msgstr "But one who, whether standing or walking,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.11:11.2"
msgid "Nisinno uda vā sayaṃ;"
msgstr "sitting or lying down,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.11:11.3"
msgid "Vitakkaṃ samayitvāna,"
msgstr "has calmed their thoughts,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.11:11.4"
msgid "Vitakkūpasame rato;"
msgstr "loving peace of mind;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.11:11.5"
msgid "Bhabbo so tādiso bhikkhu,"
msgstr "such a mendicant is capable"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.11:11.6"
msgid "Phuṭṭhuṃ sambodhimuttaman”ti."
msgstr "of touching the highest awakening.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.11:11.7"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
